cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR 

This paper focuses on facial expression recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed Spatio-Temporal Adaptive Pooling (STAP) network is a deep learning model, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the challenges of class imbalance and small databases, which are common issues in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
